@startuml Companies Flow - Current

title ProspectOS Web - Companies List and Detail Flow

actor User as U
participant "CompaniesPage" as CP
participant "CompanyDetailPage" as CDP
participant "Company API" as API

U -> CP: Open /companies
CP -> API: GET /api/companies
API --> CP: Company list
CP --> U: Render table

U -> CP: Click company row
CP -> CDP: Navigate /companies/{id}
CDP -> API: GET /api/companies/{id}
API --> CDP: Company detail
CDP --> U: Render detail card

alt Invalid id format
    CDP --> U: Show invalid id error
else API error
    CDP --> U: Show load error + retry
end

@enduml
